      "text": "Motivation is the fuel upon which all hobby projects run. This page explores ways to maximize it. In the past I have used the term \"taming the muse\", but I think I now prefer \"hacking motivation\" as it asserts more of a feeling of control over the process."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
